					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-6697939#post-3891602</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-6697939/your-guard#post-3891602</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Mon, 30 Jul 2018 17:30:18 +0000</pubDate>
								<wikidot:authorUserId>2303803</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <blockquote> <p>I took out my gun, and unloaded my entire clip right into that thing's head.</p> </blockquote> <p>You probably mean magazine, assuming it's a pistol. <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Clip_(firearms)">This is a clip.</a> Video games have made people forget the difference, grumble grumble.</p> <p>Anyway, other than the nitpick, I really like this. First-person accounts are underrated.</p> <p>Edit:</p> <blockquote> <p>I did the Overseer's dirt work quickly, effectively, and painlessly.</p> </blockquote> <p>Should be 'dirty work'?</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
